fields.name: Salty, like the tears of your enemy

data.text: 1 Saleor is a rapidly growing all-out commerce API. Saleor is fully open-source, and 100% focused on the GraphQL interface. Our mission is to provide unparalleled extensibility.
2 We make it easy for front-end teams to prototype fast, experiment, and build wonderful, unrestricted storefront experiences.
3 We enable developers to extend Saleor easily via [Saleor Apps](https://github.com/saleor/saleor-app-template), a robust tally of async/sync webhooks, and a composable Dashboard.
4 We allow brands to own their data and go fast while staying fully flexible with Saleor Cloud.
